  <brief_title>Copeptin as a Biomarker for Central Diabetes Insipidus Development Following Pituitary Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Copeptin as a Biomarker for Central Diabetes Insipidus Development Following Pituitary Surgery</official_title>
